"```sql\nSELECT AVG(pa.long_shots) AS average_long_shots\nFROM Player_Attributes pa\nJOIN Player p ON pa.player_fifa_api_id = p.player_fifa_api_id\nWHERE p.player_name = 'Ahmed Samir Farag';\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the average number of long shots for the player named \"Ahmed Samir Farag\" by joining the `Player_Attributes` and `Player` tables using the `player_fifa_api_id` as the foreign key."